summary: Re-upload to Nexus due to no one having put it here.
descriptionHtml:
The ring acts as a replacer to the Ring of Namira and gives some stealth properties. there isn\'t much description given as i haven\'t been able to play in-game with the mod. I only posted due to the fact it not being in the nexus and because a person on youtube said he had the file and people couldn\'t find it on nexus if anyone feels they could give a good description please comment and ill edit the description.
